---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 140
By: Milarepa
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Detachment From Place and
    Conditions
Format: verse
---
Native land, and home, and all possessions,
I know you all to be but empty things;
Any thoughtless one may have you.
As for me, the devotee, I go to win the Eternal Truth.
